  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc0\u0baa\u0bc1?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ranil Mustibu to release Ranjan?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to reports, Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe has instructed Justice Minister Vijayadasa Rajapaksa to prepare necessary documents for presidential pardon to former Member of Parliament Ranjan Ramanayake.",
        "Ministers Harin Fernando and Manusha Nanayakkara met the acting President and requested him to speed up the amnesty process for Ranjan.",
        "Accordingly, it is reported that the President has instructed Justice Minister Vijayadasa Rajapaksa to follow the appropriate legal procedures and expedite these proceedings.",
        "It is noteworthy that Ranjan Ramanayake, who was found guilty of contempt of court, is serving a prison sentence."
      ],
